libadalang-tools: This package contains serveral libadalang-based development tools
libadalang-tools: for Ada:
libadalang-tools:  * gnatpp      a prettry-printer to reformat source code.
libadalang-tools:  * gnatmetric  computes various source code metrics.  
libadalang-tools:  * gnatstub    creates body stub for libary unit declarations.
libadalang-tools:  * gnattest    creates unit-test skeletons as well as a test driver
libadalang-tools:                infrastructre.
